{"tid":2035064,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果： 港協暨奧委會承認選擇泳手入港隊不會理游泳時間 只會理賽事名次 並認泳手並不知情","createTime":"2020-05-25T15:34:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T05:40:01.000Z","uid":22556,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"29a67288656059d7161505e8ce9b400baa4905cf","tid":2035064,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T15:34:56.000Z","msg":"立法會帳委會今早就問題展開聆訊。港協暨奧委會行政總監鄭國鴻在追問下披露，會方考慮的「最佳成績」是指賽事名次，而非做出時間，更明言不知道有關泳手「係咪全港最快」，又推說向運動員解釋遴選準則是總會責任，即使未有公開全部準則，仍覺得對運動員「公道」，在議員炮轟下才改稱做法「唔理想」。<br />\n<br />\n詳情 ：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200525/OHQUCC3LIDP26PNC36XMGS5P2Y/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200525%2FOHQUCC3LIDP26PNC36XMGS5P2Y%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=tjA1itiRAyOaH4WNB6QjY4tKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=7c6f094a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200525%2FOHQUCC3LIDP26PNC36XMGS5P2Y%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=766dbd40\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200525/OHQUCC3LIDP26PNC36XMGS5P2Y/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"9d62b41ffcde141bf623a5dcb75c8d28f6a7a5aa","tid":2035064,"uid":76591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T15:36:07.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"3dd9047af021828bb850de326617723e58c778ee","tid":2035064,"uid":43173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T03:09:57.000Z","msg":"是但啦，都係俾香港奧委會坐飛機遊吓埠啫"},{"pid":"804618a2f4c9bd25548af7885c565652ce41b15b","tid":2035064,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci